## Final Steps

1. **Commit Your Changes:**
   - After customizing your `README.md`, scroll down to the **"Commit changes"** section.
   - Add a commit message like **"Update profile README"**.
   - Click **"Commit changes"** to save.

2. **Verify on Your Profile:**
   - Navigate to your GitHub profile by clicking on your profile picture and selecting **"Your profile"**.
   - You should see your new README displayed prominently on your profile page.

